name: b'Turnbull & Asser Ribbed Silk Tie'
desc:
b'Each Turnbull & Asser silk tie is individually handmade in London, England to ensure high quality and an impeccable finish. Its ribbed appearance will add subtle flair to your most formal looks. Shown here with a Charvet shirt . The slimmer width of this tie is exclusively for MR PORTER.

name: b'Charvet Knitted Silk Tie'
desc:
b'Heritage Parisian company Charvet is globally renowned for its high quality materials and expert construction, aptly demonstrated by this impeccable knitted silk tie. This piece is flawlessly constructed in Italy in a slim profile that works best with streamlined silhouettes. Gift it to the gentleman who appreciates luxurious details with panache.   • Dry clean
  • Made in Italy
'

name: b'Lanvin Knitted Silk Bow Tie'
desc:

  • Pre-tied style, adjustable neck strap
  • Hook and eye fastening
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in France
'

desc:
b"This splendid Drake's tie has been hand sewn, dyed and assembled in London. The navy and white polka pattern is sure to be a modern classic, contrast it against a check or striped shirt for the most stylish take. Shown here with a Charvet tie .
  • Navy silk tie
  • White polka-dot print
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Handmade in London, England
"

name: b'Lanvin Knitted Silk Tie'
desc:
b"Inject smart outfits with a splash of opulent colour with Lanvin 's grape tie. Knitted in Italy from lustrous silk, it makes a dapper impression worn against any shade. Shown here with a Charvet shirt .
  • Grape knitted silk tie
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in Italy
"

name: b'Brioni Knitted Silk Tie'
desc:
b"Knitted ties are a classic addition to any wardrobe and this hand-finished version from Brioni will bring an air of finesse to any outfit. The easy-to-wear light blue hue goes superbly with crisp whites and soft pinks - team it with these colour palettes for an accomplished look. Shown here with a Charvet shirt .

  • Small 'b' logo
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Handmade in Italy
"

name: b'Brooks Brothers Silk Double Bow Tie'
desc:
b'Having dressed the likes of Presidents John F. Kennedy and Abraham Lincoln, American label Brooks Brothers is a fail-safe choice for formal occasions. For an evening formula that will guarantee sartorial success, team this impeccable silk double bow tie with a bib-front shirt and a tuxedo.

  • Adjustable strap, pre-tied style
  • Hook and eye fastening
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in the USA
'

name: b'Turnbull & Asser Silk Bow Tie'
desc:
b'When choosing a bow tie for a black tie outfit, a foolproof tip is to match your tie to the lapel of your jacket. In the case of this self-tie Turnbull & Asser design, opt for a silk lapel with a slight sheen. A dress shirt, blazer and Cary Grant swagger will take you through the evening in impeccable style.

  • Self-tie style, adjustable red grosgrain strap
  • Clip fastening
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in England
'

desc:
b"Meticulously made in England from fine mulberry silk, Alfred Dunhill 's sleek silk tie typifies the British company's dedication to superlative craftsmanship. This dapper piece comes in an understated two-tone pattern complete with neatly stitched stripes adding a dash of flair to your sharp city line-up. Shown here with a Charvet shirt .

  • Dry clean
  • Made in England
"

  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
